  user_input {
    user_response: "# Oasis Resort Document Centre \342\200\224 File Hosting Inventory\n\nThis document provides an inventory and overview of the file hosting system deployed on the Azure Virtual Machine (`9.205.155.61`).\n\n---\n\n## System Architecture Overview\n\n*   **Physical Root Directory**: `/var/www/una/repository/` (owned by `www-data:www-data`)\n*   **Web Server Handler**: Nginx, which aliases the repository directory for static assets\n*   **API Router**: A custom PHP REST handler at `/docs/index.php` that serves folder structure listings, download handles, file upload intakes, and deletion requests.\n\n---\n\n## API Access Endpoints\n\n| Operation | HTTP Method | Endpoint | Authorization |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| **Browse Root Folders** | GET | `http://9.205.155.61/docs/?api=1&action=browse` | Public (No Auth) |\n| **Browse Subfolder** | GET | `http://9.205.155.61/docs/?api=1&action=browse&path={folder}` | Public (No Auth) |\n| **Download File** | GET | `http://9.205.155.61/docs/?api=1&action=download&path={filepath}` | Public (No Auth) |\n| **Upload Files** | POST | `http://9.205.155.61/docs/?api=1&action=upload&path={folder}` | Requires `X-Admin-Token` |\n| **Delete File/Folder** | DELETE | `http://9.205.155.61/docs/?api=1&action=delete&path={filepath}` | Requires `X-Admin-Token` |\n| **Create Folder** | POST | `http://9.205.155.61/docs/?api=1&action=mkdir&path=` | Requires `X-Admin-Token` |\n\n---\n\n## Directory Layout & File List\n\nBelow is a complete, live list of all folders, files, sizes, and system ownership details currently stored in the repository.\n\n### \360\237\223\201 Root Directory (`/var/www/una/repository/`)\n\n| File / Folder Name | Type | Size | Last Modified | Permissions |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| `Board-Minutes/` | Directory | \342\200\224 | 2026-05-12 17:55 | `drwxr-xr-x` (www-data) |\n| `Financial-Statements/` | Directory | \342\200\224 | 2026-05-29 22:40 | `drwxr-xr-x` (www-data) |\n| `Forms/` | Directory | \342\200\224 | 2026-05-12 17:55 | `drwxr-xr-x` (www-data) |\n| `Insurance/` | Directory | \342\200\224 | 2026-05-12 17:55 | `drwxr-xr-x` (www-data) |\n| `.htaccess` | File | 98 B | 2026-05-12 17:31 | `-rw-r--r--` (www-data) |\n\n---\n\n### \360\237\223\202 Folder: `Board-Minutes`\n\n| File Name | Format | Size (Bytes) | Size (KB) | Last Modified |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| `January-13-2026-Board-minutes.pdf` | PDF | 469,346 B | 458.3 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n| `Sept-13-2025-AGM-Minutes.pdf` | PDF | 139,945 B | 136.6 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n\n---\n\n### \360\237\223\202 Folder: `Financial-Statements`\n\n> [!NOTE]\n> This folder is currently **empty**. There are no documents hosted in this section.\n\n---\n\n### \360\237\223\202 Folder: `Forms`\n\n| File Name | Format | Size (Bytes) | Size (KB) | Last Modified |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| `Oasis-Form-for-Non-Paying-Guests-Fillable.pdf` | PDF | 841,596 B | 821.8 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n| `Oasis-Form-for-Renters-Fillable.pdf` | PDF | 829,278 B | 809.8 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n| `Development-Permit-and-Process-2019-Fillable-1.pdf` | PDF | 702,842 B | 686.3 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n| `Tree-Application-2019-Fillable.pdf` | PDF | 661,009 B | 645.5 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n| `Development-Permit-and-Process-2019-Fillable.pdf` | PDF | 143,260 B | 139.9 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n| `Oasis-RV-Resort-Buoy-Rental-Waiver-Form.pdf` | PDF | 38,229 B | 37.3 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n\n---\n\n### \360\237\223\202 Folder: `Insurance`\n\n| File Name | Format | Size (Bytes) | Size (KB) | Last Modified |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| `Oasis.Q1.2026.pdf` | PDF | 597,250 B | 583.2 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n| `Oasis.Q2.NTR_.pdf` | PDF | 182,879 B | 178.6 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |"
    items {
      text: "# Oasis Resort Document Centre \342\200\224 File Hosting Inventory\n\nThis document provides an inventory and overview of the file hosting system deployed on the Azure Virtual Machine (`9.205.155.61`).\n\n---\n\n## System Architecture Overview\n\n*   **Physical Root Directory**: `/var/www/una/repository/` (owned by `www-data:www-data`)\n*   **Web Server Handler**: Nginx, which aliases the repository directory for static assets\n*   **API Router**: A custom PHP REST handler at `/docs/index.php` that serves folder structure listings, download handles, file upload intakes, and deletion requests.\n\n---\n\n## API Access Endpoints\n\n| Operation | HTTP Method | Endpoint | Authorization |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| **Browse Root Folders** | GET | `http://9.205.155.61/docs/?api=1&action=browse` | Public (No Auth) |\n| **Browse Subfolder** | GET | `http://9.205.155.61/docs/?api=1&action=browse&path={folder}` | Public (No Auth) |\n| **Download File** | GET | `http://9.205.155.61/docs/?api=1&action=download&path={filepath}` | Public (No Auth) |\n| **Upload Files** | POST | `http://9.205.155.61/docs/?api=1&action=upload&path={folder}` | Requires `X-Admin-Token` |\n| **Delete File/Folder** | DELETE | `http://9.205.155.61/docs/?api=1&action=delete&path={filepath}` | Requires `X-Admin-Token` |\n| **Create Folder** | POST | `http://9.205.155.61/docs/?api=1&action=mkdir&path=` | Requires `X-Admin-Token` |\n\n---\n\n## Directory Layout & File List\n\nBelow is a complete, live list of all folders, files, sizes, and system ownership details currently stored in the repository.\n\n### \360\237\223\201 Root Directory (`/var/www/una/repository/`)\n\n| File / Folder Name | Type | Size | Last Modified | Permissions |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| `Board-Minutes/` | Directory | \342\200\224 | 2026-05-12 17:55 | `drwxr-xr-x` (www-data) |\n| `Financial-Statements/` | Directory | \342\200\224 | 2026-05-29 22:40 | `drwxr-xr-x` (www-data) |\n| `Forms/` | Directory | \342\200\224 | 2026-05-12 17:55 | `drwxr-xr-x` (www-data) |\n| `Insurance/` | Directory | \342\200\224 | 2026-05-12 17:55 | `drwxr-xr-x` (www-data) |\n| `.htaccess` | File | 98 B | 2026-05-12 17:31 | `-rw-r--r--` (www-data) |\n\n---\n\n### \360\237\223\202 Folder: `Board-Minutes`\n\n| File Name | Format | Size (Bytes) | Size (KB) | Last Modified |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| `January-13-2026-Board-minutes.pdf` | PDF | 469,346 B | 458.3 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n| `Sept-13-2025-AGM-Minutes.pdf` | PDF | 139,945 B | 136.6 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n\n---\n\n### \360\237\223\202 Folder: `Financial-Statements`\n\n> [!NOTE]\n> This folder is currently **empty**. There are no documents hosted in this section.\n\n---\n\n### \360\237\223\202 Folder: `Forms`\n\n| File Name | Format | Size (Bytes) | Size (KB) | Last Modified |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| `Oasis-Form-for-Non-Paying-Guests-Fillable.pdf` | PDF | 841,596 B | 821.8 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n| `Oasis-Form-for-Renters-Fillable.pdf` | PDF | 829,278 B | 809.8 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n| `Development-Permit-and-Process-2019-Fillable-1.pdf` | PDF | 702,842 B | 686.3 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n| `Tree-Application-2019-Fillable.pdf` | PDF | 661,009 B | 645.5 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n| `Development-Permit-and-Process-2019-Fillable.pdf` | PDF | 143,260 B | 139.9 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n| `Oasis-RV-Resort-Buoy-Rental-Waiver-Form.pdf` | PDF | 38,229 B | 37.3 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n\n---\n\n### \360\237\223\202 Folder: `Insurance`\n\n| File Name | Format | Size (Bytes) | Size (KB) | Last Modified |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| `Oasis.Q1.2026.pdf` | PDF | 597,250 B | 583.2 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |\n| `Oasis.Q2.NTR_.pdf` | PDF | 182,879 B | 178.6 KB | 2026-05-12 17:55 |"
    }
  }
}
