  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Considering Visual Refinements**\n\nI\'m now focusing on visual refinements, specifically a \"newer Mac\" aesthetic with a glass effect. My initial exploration centers on achieving blurred, translucent backgrounds using a backdrop-blur. I\'m keen on how this will integrate with the existing design elements.\n\n\n**Implementing Visual Tweaks**\n\nI\'m now implementing visual tweaks focusing on glass-like effects using Tailwind classes like `bg-white/70` with `backdrop-blur-xl`. I\'m also considering vibrant desktop wallpapers, and have updated the `body` background to use a visually appealing Unsplash image. I\'m actively modifying `src/components/DesktopWindow.tsx` and evaluating the integration of these effects within the existing UI.\n\n\n**Refining Translucent Elements**\n\nI\'m now refining the translucent elements, especially the title bar and main content area. Using Tailwind classes like `bg-white/70` and `backdrop-blur-2xl` is allowing me to achieve the desired effect. I\'m actively integrating these changes across `DesktopWindow.tsx` and `App.tsx` and evaluating their visual impact on the overall design.\n\n\n**Adjusting for Contrast**\n\nI\'m now adjusting backgrounds to be translucent with a semi-transparent white. Dark text provides good contrast. I\'ve updated `SidebarTree.tsx` to include `bg-white/60` and `text-blue-600` for active items. Also updated `FileViewerModal.tsx` for translucent effects. I\'m also planning to update App.tsx icons for a similar glass aesthetic.\n\n\n**Enhancing Button Appearances**\n\nI\'m now enhancing button appearances. The plan is to edit several components. I am using `bg-white/50`, `focus:bg-white`, `focus:ring-blue-400`, `border border-white/40`, and `shadow-sm` for the base style. I will update `DesktopWindow.tsx` and similar components with these refined visual styles. I\'m also adding `bg-white/50 hover:bg-white/80` with a subtle ring and shadow effect to the \'back\' button style.\n\n\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 11
      nanos: 479948613
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
